It has recently expanded to the iOS platform with an app for iPhone users. The release of the new version of this app - also available on Android - is part of the Connect-Tech project. Better governance through tech Sponsored by Making All Voices Count, a consortium of funders making grants available to support innovation and technology, the Connect-Tech project is part of a movement to support better governance through technology You can search for your nearest public services in South Africa, India, Nigeria, Ghana, Kenya and Mauritius - with ratings from thousands of users&#x2019; personal experiences. The public is invited to join the community and share their real experiences, on the go, by adding your ratings and reviews. Problems with service delivery in your community? Rate it, review it and your municipality will take action.